# Readme

This is a puppet-module to install (or remove) a tomcat instance and deploy one or more webapplications. Tested and developed on RHEL and CentOS.


To get started; Download tomcat and place it in the files directory:
$ wget http://www.eu.apache.org/dist/tomcat/tomcat-7/v7.0.39/bin/apache-tomcat-7.0.39.tar.gz -O /files/apache-tomcat-7.0.39.tar.gz


Adjust $tomcat::params::tomcatversion to the tomcat version you plan on using.

Adjust  params.pp to match your setup.
